                Mr. Benjamin Smith
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-7aed283f-657b-48f1-80f4-7928b9dfb519" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
